rows.label: qst501803_msg0001
rows.name:
How terrible... That precious tome...
I must apologize to my client...

rows.label: qst501803_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh, hello there. Who are you?
Are you acquainted with a Blade
named Shiki, by any chance?

rows.label: qst501803_msg0003
rows.name:
There's something I need to tell her,
so if you could bring her to me,
I would be most grateful.

rows.label: qst501803_msg0011
rows.name:
The ship which was supposed to be
delivering a Tome of Mors was
sunk in the waters near Gula.

rows.label: qst501803_msg0012
rows.name:
You might be able to salvage it near
Umon's Shipyard. There's no guarantee
though.
